==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: The eighteen changes of a grown woman.

===Pronunciation===
*[[Pinyin]]: nǚ dà shí bā biàn

===Idiom===
'''[[女]][[大]][[十]][[八]][[變]]'''

# All of the changes that a girl makes when turning into a woman.

#: ''[[小時候]]，[[徐]][[媽媽]][[對]][[自己]][[這個]][[難看]][[的]][[小]][[女兒]][[十分]][[失望]]。[[但是]]，'''女大十八變'''，[[小S]][[如今]][[已經]][[成為]][[亭亭玉立]][[的]][[小天鵝]]。''

===Alternate forms===
[[女大十八变]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

